# 📚 Django Bookstore Project

This is a simple Django web application for managing and displaying a list of books. The project demonstrates core Django concepts like models, templates, views, URL routing, admin panel usage, and database interaction.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Home page displaying all books
- Admin panel to add/update/delete books
- Book model with fields: `title`, `author`, `price`
- Clean template structure for future expansion

---

## 📂 Project Structure

bookstore/
├── bookstore/ # Django project settings
├── store/ # Django app with models, views, templates
├── templates/ # HTML templates
├── db.sqlite3 # SQLite database
├── manage.py # Django project manager
├── venv/ # Virtual environment (excluded from Git)
└── .gitignore # Git ignore file

yaml
Copy code

---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack

- Python 3.10+
- Django 5.x
- SQLite (default database)
- HTML (for templates)

---

